data.description: Beautiful and Meticulously cared for, 3 bedroom and 3 bath Ranch home. Open Floor plan with Hardwood Floors, Vaulted Ceiling in Family Room with Stone Fireplace. Large Dining room, Gorgeous Kitchen with Stainless Steel Appliances. New Garbage disposal. Kitchen cabinets with pull out drawers. Large Master bedroom with Trey Ceiling, Walk in closets, Double Vanity, Omega Bidet, Garden Tub and Separate Shower. Split bedroom Plan, Spacious Breakfast area, Partial finished basement with a Full bath, Bonus rooms and plenty of room for storage. Main HVAC system new. Charming Sunscreen Porch and Trex deck and over looking a Private backyard. In Sought after North Paulding Cedarcrest Area! Close to shopping and entertainment. Motivated Seller! NO H.O.A
